// §5.11.2 Float to string edge cases - A3 spec update makes these
// byte-identical at conformance level Full.

neg_zero is -0.0 to string
pos_zero is 0.0 to string
infty is (1.0 / 0.0) to string
neg_infty is (-1.0 / 0.0) to string
nan_val is (0.0 / 0.0) to string
plain is 3.14 to string
tiny is 1.0e-6 to string
sci_large is 1.0e100 to string
